channel.title: Impozzes V2! Zombies Minigame! Abby Vine Whip! Lottery! Webclient Ready! Diceing
channel.description:
[IMG]http://i1103.photobucket.com/albums/g477/totalystylin/ImpozzesV2Banner.png[/img]
[IMG]http://i1103.photobucket.com/albums/g477/totalystylin/Please-Comment-3.gif[/img]
[IMG]http://i1103.photobucket.com/albums/g477/totalystylin/PleaseVote.gif[/img]
Well guys, i've been working on this server for a few months, and I think it's ready for release! I would host it, but I have alot of school to catch up on. But anyways, haters will hate. :P :P :P
This is Originally InsidiaX
Things I have done:
Fixed Alot of bugs. Added Zombies Minigame! Added Green Donator Cape which gives x2 Xp in All Skills! Added Red Donator Cape which gives x3 Xp in All Skills! Fixed a Few pouches for summoning! (now 90% summoning) Donator Points Added! (::givepoints (playername) (amount) Zombie Minigame Points (A.K.A PfPoints (PF = Player Friendly)) :D:D Fixed Total Level!!!! And MUCH, MUCH MORE!
Fixed Skill Tab Hovers! [IMG]http://i1103.photobucket.com/albums/g477/totalystylin/Workingskilltabhovers.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i1103.photobucket.com/albums/g477/totalystylin/SkillTabHover2.jpg[/img]
Total Level Fixed! [IMG]http://i1103.photobucket.com/albums/g477/totalystylin/TotalLevel1.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i1103.photobucket.com/albums/g477/totalystylin/TotalLevel2.jpg[/img]
Zombies Minigame! [IMG]http://i1103.photobucket.com/albums/g477/totalystylin/Zombieminigame.jpg[/img]
Added Lottery!! [IMG]http://i1103.photobucket.com/albums/g477/totalystylin/Lottery1.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i1103.photobucket.com/albums/g477/totalystylin/Lottery2.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i1103.photobucket.com/albums/g477/totalystylin/Lottery3.jpg[/img]
Added Death Cape! [IMG]http://i1103.photobucket.com/albums/g477/totalystylin/DeathCape.jpg[/img]
And a special emote for it! [URL=http://picasion.com/][IMG]http://i.picasion.com/pic50/f37389a6482da78fefbc118268a97a08.gif[/img][/URL][URL=http://picasion.com/][/URL]
Added Abyssal Vine Whip! [IMG]http://i1103.photobucket.com/albums/g477/totalystylin/AbbysalVineWhip.jpg[/img]
And a Special Attack! [IMG]http://i1103.photobucket.com/albums/g477/totalystylin/AbbyVineWhipSpec.jpg[/img]
Added Donator Shop! (items cost donator points). + Added Green And Red Donor Capes! (Green gives x2 xp, Red gives x3) [IMG]http://i1103.photobucket.com/albums/g477/totalystylin/DonatorPointShop.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i1103.photobucket.com/albums/g477/totalystylin/QuestTab.jpg[/img]
Login message. Lol. [IMG]http://i1103.photobucket.com/albums/g477/totalystylin/LoginMessage.jpg[/img]
Made player shops available for only Players, Mods, and Donators. (Incase of staff abuse) [IMG]http://i1103.photobucket.com/albums/g477/totalystylin/Playershoprank.jpg[/img]
Goal: 50 Downloads [X] 100 Downloads [X] 200 Downloads [X] 250 Downloads [X] 300 Downloads [X] 400 Downloads [X] 500 Downloads [X] 750 Downloads [X] 1000 Downloads [X] 1500 Downloads [X] 2500 Downloads [X]
Download:
Client Download - http://uppit.com/au63hvf3ftsz/Impozzes_Client_v2.rar Source Download - http://uppit.com/btln2idxclu8/Impozzes_Source_v2.rar Package Download - http://uppit.com/u105b5xlq9xb/Impozzes_v2_Package.rar
Credits: InsidiaX - 50% Me - 50%
My Skype: ninja_rapeist
Commonly asked Questions:
Q. How do I change the source Ip? A. Search server.java in the folder, and open it. Then search 127.0.0.1 in server.java. Change 127.0.0.1 to your Wanted Ip.
Q. How do i change the Client Ip? A. Search client.java in the folder, and open it. Then search 127.0.0.1 in client.java. Change 127.0.0.1 to your Wanted Ip.
Q. My run doesn't work. How do i fix it? A. Go to Start > Computer > C: Drive > Program Files > Java. Then go back to your run > right click > edit, and change the jdk to yours.
Hope you enjoy! And agin, Haters will hate! :P
